
  <section id="uuid-tool" class="section">
    <h2>UUID Generator</h2>
    <p>A UUID (Universally Unique Identifier) is used to generate a unique identifier. Each version has a different generation method and purpose.</p>
    <div class="uuid-generator">
      <div class="uuid-version">
        <h3>UUID v4 (Random-based)</h3>
        <p>Completely randomly generated and widely used. The possibility of collision is extremely low.</p>
        <button id="generate-uuid-v4">Generate UUID v4</button>
        <p><strong>Result:</strong> <span id="uuid-v4-result">00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000</span>
          <button class="copy-btn">Copy</button></p>
      </div>
      <div class="uuid-version">
        <h3>UUID v7 (Sortable by Time)</h3>
        <p>Generated by combining a Unix timestamp with a random value. It is sortable by time and advantageous for database indexing.</p>
        <button id="generate-uuid-v7">Generate UUID v7</button>
        <p><strong>Result:</strong> <span id="uuid-v7-result">00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000</span>
          <button class="copy-btn">Copy</button></p>
      </div>
      <div class="uuid-version">
        <h3>UUID v1 (Time-based)</h3>
        <p>Generated based on the current time and MAC address. It is unique but may expose time information.</p>
        <button id="generate-uuid-v1">Generate UUID v1</button>
        <p><strong>Result:</strong> <span id="uuid-v1-result">00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000</span>
          <button class="copy-btn">Copy</button></p>
      </div>
      <div class="uuid-version">
        <h3>UUID v5 (Name-based, SHA-1)</h3>
        <p>Generated by converting a namespace and name string into an SHA-1 hash. It is more secure than v3.</p>
        <label for="uuid-v5-namespace">Namespace:</label>
        <input type="text" id="uuid-v5-namespace" placeholder="e.g., 6ba7b810-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8">
        <label for="uuid-v5-name">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="uuid-v5-name" placeholder="e.g., my-unique-name">
        <button id="generate-uuid-v5">Generate UUID v5</button>
        <p><strong>Result:</strong> <span id="uuid-v5-result">00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000</span>
          <button class="copy-btn">Copy</button></p>
      </div>
      <div class="uuid-version">
        <h3>UUID v3 (Name-based, MD5)</h3>
        <p>Generated by converting a namespace and name string into an MD5 hash. It always produces the same result for the same input.</p>
        <label for="uuid-v3-namespace">Namespace:</label>
        <input type="text" id="uuid-v3-namespace" placeholder="e.g., 6ba7b810-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8">
        <label for="uuid-v3-name">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="uuid-v3-name" placeholder="e.g., my-unique-name">
        <button id="generate-uuid-v3">Generate UUID v3</button>
        <p><strong>Result:</strong> <span id="uuid-v3-result">00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000</span>
          <button class="copy-btn">Copy</button></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

